{"word":"ἀνακόπτω","slug":"ἀνακόπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακόπτω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to drive back</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to beat back</i> an assailant, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to stop:—</i> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be stopped, stop short</i>, <el>τινός</el> <i>from</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}